    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outlaw Raiders 是一款融合了 Roguelike 元素的战略自动战斗游戏。率领你的亡命徒团队进行抢劫、偷盗和战斗，获取财富。建设你的营地并招募更多亡命徒，成为终极亡命之王。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/e3769b9051f0b2807e02f14be6a694ee.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ae619bc810a33c8686328c1323750bad.poster.avif?t=1769600510\" width=780 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ae619bc810a33c8686328c1323750bad.webm?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ae619bc810a33c8686328c1323750bad.mp4?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在伏击毫无防备的旅人时，策略至关重要。Outlaw Raiders 允许你以自己的风格策划战略伏击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/7c925b72135f8c3a1c98c5f9e37fd640.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/1a14aae364ad5e3c37851664e78e4397.poster.avif?t=1769600510\" width=780 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/1a14aae364ad5e3c37851664e78e4397.webm?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/1a14aae364ad5e3c37851664e78e4397.mp4?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人也有确保安全通行的策略。仔细观察敌方巡逻，寻找最佳的进攻时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/56a23d7f6bc02618dda10538b49cb1bf.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ccc56d8d175e78dd1bbdc519abf4dce1.poster.avif?t=1769600510\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ccc56d8d175e78dd1bbdc519abf4dce1.webm?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/ccc56d8d175e78dd1bbdc519abf4dce1.mp4?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你觉得时机成熟时，下达攻击指令，可以一次性派出全部单位，或分批进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/4d2e21b392974e26aebf42465dbf116e.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/0b7626a041029ab62445fe8cc54011b2.poster.avif?t=1769600510\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/0b7626a041029ab62445fe8cc54011b2.webm?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/0b7626a041029ab62445fe8cc54011b2.mp4?t=1769600510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越道路。每一次冒险都会带来全新的路线，包含分支选择、危险遭遇、事件与奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/0b5a298ab1e33b14d4b67b0d2a975735.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/eaac586226180f495edc11fba933e170.avif?t=1769600510\" width=780 height=419 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使是亡命徒，也需要一个称之为家的地方。扩建你的营地，解锁新的建筑与更多亡命徒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/1b46a2a815da0f3b4cc4db37758cefab.avif?t=1769600510\" width=615 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367460/extras/3309bf9fd203206f0911afa6b570570f.avif?t=1769600510\" width=955 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 4 位指挥官中进行选择，每位指挥官都拥有独特的玩法、事件和单位。</p>",
